php-sfcgal NEWS
===============

1.0.1 — gap-fix release
  - SFCGALGeometry::BUFFER3D_{ROUND,CYLSPHERE,FLAT} class constants
    (mirror sfcgal_buffer3d_type_t).
  - SFCGALMultiPoint / MultiLineString / MultiPolygon / MultiSolid now
    extend SFCGALGeometryCollection (per OGC SF), so they inherit
    addGeometry() / setGeometryN(). Fixes the "addGeometry not found
    on MultiPolygon" oversight.
  - SFCGALMultiSolid::create() factory now actually registered.
  - New: SFCGALGeometry::decomposeToFaces(): SFCGALMultiPolygon —
    flatten Solid / PolyhedralSurface / TriangulatedSurface /
    MultiSolid / Triangle to a MultiPolygon Z of face polygons.
  - toGEOS() auto-decomposes 3D-only types via decomposeToFaces() then
    emits MultiPolygon Z WKB. Fixes "Solid asWkb fails" upstream block
    and "GEOS Unknown WKB type 15" PolyhedralSurface block.
  - fromGEOS() now sets GEOSWKBWriter::setFlavor(GEOSWKB_ISO) on the
    internal writer, so the WKB SFCGAL receives is in the format it
    parses (not EWKB).
  - Internal: explicit __construct invocation on the GEOSWKBWriter /
    GEOSWKBReader proxy objects (php-geos's constructors initialise the
    relay; object_init_ex alone is not enough).
  - tests/009_BridgeAndDecompose.phpt — regression coverage for all of
    the above. Suite now 10/10 green.

1.0.0 — initial release (target: 2026-Q2)
  - PHP bindings for SFCGAL 2.2.0 ISO 19107:2013 / OGC SFA 1.2 3D operations
  - SFCGALGeometry hierarchy (flat global names, matching php-geos style):
    SFCGALPoint, SFCGALLineString, SFCGALPolygon, SFCGALMultiPoint,
    SFCGALMultiLineString, SFCGALMultiPolygon, SFCGALGeometryCollection,
    SFCGALTriangle, SFCGALTriangulatedSurface, SFCGALPolyhedralSurface,
    SFCGALSolid, SFCGALMultiSolid
  - SFCGALPreparedGeometry (SRID-bearing wrapper)
  - I/O: WKT, EWKT, WKB, hex-WKB, OBJ, STL, VTK, binary prepared
  - 3D predicates: intersects3D, covers3D, isPlanar, isAlmostEquals
  - 3D measures: area3D, length3D, volume, centroid3D, distance3D, envelope3D
  - 3D set ops: intersection3D, difference3D, union3D, convexHull3D
  - Mesh ops: tesselate, extrude, makeSolid, triangulate2DZ
  - Skeleton family: straightSkeleton, approximateMedialAxis,
    extrudeStraightSkeleton, extrudePolygonStraightSkeleton,
    straightSkeletonPartition, offsetPolygon
  - Buffers: buffer3D (with type enum), minkowskiSum
  - Alpha: alphaShapes, optimalAlphaShapes, alphaWrapping3D
  - Visibility: visibilityPoint, visibilitySegment
  - Transforms: forceZ, forceM, dropZ, dropM, forceLHR, forceRHR, swapXY,
    rotate*, scale*, translate*, round, simplify, lineSubstring
  - Partition_2 family
  - Bridge to/from \GEOS\Geometry via WKB round-trip
  - Full PHPT/PHPUnit test corpus + ported PostGIS regress/sfcgal/*.sql
